# Accounting View Reconciliation

The platform records every accounting event as a row in
`accounting_invoices` + `accounting_payments`, but the **policy
obligation** is NOT the sum of those rows. Client-direct payments and
agent settlements are **alternative payment paths** for the SAME
obligation, not two independent debts. The canonical reconciled view
is produced by `/api/accounting/statements/by-policy/:policyId` and
rendered by `<StatementPaymentCard>`.

